&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&amp;nbsp;We are hiring an Afternoon Extended Day Guide for our Guidepost Montessori school at North Scottsdale!&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;At Guidepost Montessori, our Extended Day team creates a calm and joyful end to each child&#39;s day. This role is perfect for someone who loves working with children ages &lt;strong&gt;0–6&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/strong&gt;and wants to contribute to a meaningful after-school experience in a supportive environment.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Your Impact&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;As a &lt;strong&gt;Extended Day Guide&lt;/strong&gt;, you’ll support our afternoon program for children ages 0-6. You&#39;ll help create a peaceful, engaging environment where children can unwind, explore, and connect at the end of the day.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;You&#39;ll also play a key role during pick-up, helping create a warm, welcoming experience for families and ensuring each child&#39;s day ends in a calm, connected way.&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;&amp;nbsp;You&#39;ll support planned activities, help maintain a consistent routine, and contribute ideas to make the program enriching and enjoyable for children.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;What You’ll Do&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Support a calm, safe, and engaging after-school environment&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Facilitate a mix of structured and open-ended activities&amp;nbsp;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Prepare materials and maintain an orderly space&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Supervise and engage with children in a warm, respectful way&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Welcome and engage with families at pick-up, ensuring a smooth transition home and sharing relevant updates&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Partner with the school team to ensure a smooth transition from the school day to extended care&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Contribute ideas and feedback to help strengthen the extended day experience&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;What We’re Looking For&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Experience working with young children in a school, childcare, or camp setting&amp;nbsp;&lt;/li&gt;
